            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "E-ERR",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The error of E is determined  essentially  by",
                " the  error  of  the order of 2 %  connected with the",
                " spatial reconstruction, taking into account also the",
                " finite  dimension  of  the  target,   and   by   the",
                " range-energy relation. The error in the range-energy",
                " relation is assumed to be 3 %."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Corrected for:",
                " i) tracks ending outside  the  sensitive  volume  of",
                "   chamber,",
                " ii) the energy dependence of (n,alpha) elastic cross",
                "   section."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ADD-RES": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The neutron fraction for E > 2 MeV  turns out  to  be",
                " 0.03 with error 0.02 for Pb and 0.09 with error 0.03",
                " for Bi."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The experimental  energy  spectra  were analysed with",
                " the formula given by Le Couteur  and  Lang  for  the",
                " evaporative processes at high excitation energies."
              ]
            }
